# No environment variables are required for this project!
#
# All APIs used are free and keyless:
#   - Open-Meteo (weather + air quality) — https://open-meteo.com
#   - OpenStreetMap Nominatim (geocoding) — https://nominatim.org
#
# The only env var Prisma needs is the database URL (SQLite by default):
DATABASE_URL="file:./dev.db"
